parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag to be turned off, even when a passenger is present, which can lead to serious injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light is illuminated
the airbag is turned off
the airbag warning light is on
the SRS airbag system needs to be checked

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or fatality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden and unexplained windshield cracking can cause a significant obstruction to the driver's view, leading to hazardous driving conditions and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Windshield cracks or shatters without any apparent reason
often starting from the bottom or edges of the windshield
and can spread rapidly; no evidence of external damage or impact; crack may be internal to the windshield.
